Package: rotarymars-setup-ubuntu
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: curl, gnupg, software-properties-common, ca-certificates, lsb-release
Maintainer: rotarymars <s.goto2050@gmail.com>
Description: Rotarymars Ubuntu Setup Package
 A meta-package that configures apt sources, GPG keys, and installs
 all required packages for the rotarymars Ubuntu environment.
 Phase 1 (preinst): Installs GPG keys and apt sources/repositories, updates apt cache.
 Phase 2 (postinst): Installs all apt packages.
